### ==========================================
### ATTENDANCE SERVICE API TESTS
### ==========================================
### Service should be running on http://localhost:3002
### Auth service must be running on http://localhost:3001
### First, get auth token from auth service

### Step 1: Get Auth Token (Instructor)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "instructor@attendance.com",
  "password": "Instructor@123"
}

### Save the accessToken from above response as @authToken
@authToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiIxN2QyZjZkYy0xODkzLTQ0OWUtYjA3My0xODk1MDNhZjc4ZGIiLCJlbWFpbCI6Imluc3RydWN0b3JAYXR0ZW5kYW5jZS5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiSU5TVFJVQ1RPUiIsImp0aSI6IjUzYTE2MjA5LTcwNDAtNDEyNi1hMTkzLTYwNTJmOTlhMDYxMSIsImlhdCI6MTc1NjMyNTg4MywiZXhwIjoxNzU2MzI2NzgzfQ.x3Z7Qj4yzpBVGovDGMEEI05ULI5oHMmgZGGFUpp3GSs

