### ==========================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ==========================================

### Health Check - Attendance Service
GET http://localhost:3002/health

### ==========================================
### COURSE ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Create Course (Instructor only)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Course via API",
  "description": "Testing course creation through API",
  "startDate": "2025-09-01",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31",
  "settings": {
    "gpsRadius": 100,
    "allowLateEntry": true,
    "lateEntryMinutes": 20,
    "requireSelfie": false,
    "autoEndSession": true,
    "autoEndMinutes": 120
  }
}

### Get All Courses (User's enrolled courses)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Course by ID (replace with actual course ID from seeded data)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/courses/2d478290-4f37-4e39-a332-526b9283ee4b
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Join Course with Code (Student) - Use code from seeded courses
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/courses/enroll
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "CS1011AJC"
}

### Leave Course (Student)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/courses/2d478290-4f37-4e39-a332-526b9283ee4b/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

### Update Course (Instructor/Owner only)
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/v1/courses/2d478290-4f37-4e39-a332-526b9283ee4b
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Course Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### ==========================================
### SESSION ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Create Session (Instructor)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "2d478290-4f37-4e39-a332-526b9283ee4b",
  "name": "Test Session API",
  "description": "Testing session creation",
  "startTime": "2025-08-27T14:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-08-27T16:00:00Z",
  "latitude": 37.7749,
  "longitude": -122.4194,
  "radiusMeters": 75,
  "locationName": "Test Location",
  "allowLateEntry": true,
  "lateMinutes": 15,
  "requireSelfie": false
}

### Get Active Sessions
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/sessions/active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Session by ID
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/sessions/1a9b4ccb-0fb7-4b1c-a70c-8c68f6e1ff52
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Start Session (Instructor)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/sessions/1a9b4ccb-0fb7-4b1c-a70c-8c68f6e1ff52/start
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "actualLatitude": 37.7749,
  "actualLongitude": -122.4194
}

### End Session (Instructor)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/sessions/1a9b4ccb-0fb7-4b1c-a70c-8c68f6e1ff52/end
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Session completed successfully"
}

### ==========================================
### ATTENDANCE ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Mark Attendance (Student) - Session must be active, must be within GPS radius
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "1a9b4ccb-0fb7-4b1c-a70c-8c68f6e1ff52",
  "latitude": 37.7749,
  "longitude": -122.4194,
  "deviceInfo": {
    "platform": "web",
    "model": "Chrome",
    "osVersion": "Windows 11",
    "appVersion": "1.0.0"
  }
}

### Test Outside GPS Radius (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v1/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "1a9b4ccb-0fb7-4b1c-a70c-8c68f6e1ff52",
  "latitude": 37.8000,
  "longitude": -122.4500,
  "deviceInfo": {
    "platform": "web",
    "model": "Chrome",
    "osVersion": "Windows 11",
    "appVersion": "1.0.0"
  }
}

### Get Session Attendance (Instructor view)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/attendance/session/1a9b4ccb-0fb7-4b1c-a70c-8c68f6e1ff52
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get User Attendance History within enrolled course
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v1/attendance/course/2d478290-4f37-4e39-a332-526b9283ee4b/user/d68c9d80-4c4e-4fb1-aee1-46416dc4213c
Authorization: Bearer {{studentToken}}

